g="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joseph_Okpako_Kieran_Frost_JMEnternational_Andrew_Benge-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/truck-festival">卡车节</a>公布了 2025 年卡车节的第一批名字，其中四个大头条名字已锁定。</p><p>该音乐节将于 7 月 24 日至 27 日在牛津郡的 Hill 农场举行，并以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courteeners">Courteeners</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nothing-but-thieves">Nothing But Thieves</a>为主角，后者是英国独家音乐节。</p><p>门票将于周四（11月28日）下午6点开始预售，周五（11月29日）上午10点开始正式发售。周末门票起价为 150 英镑，您可以<a href="https://truckfestival.com/tickets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到您的门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3815696" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3815696" style="width: 1081px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3815696" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025.jpg" alt="" width="1081" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025.jpg 1081w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025-800x799.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025-696x695.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/truck_festival_2025-1068x1067.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1081px) 100vw, 1081px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3815696" class="wp-caption-text"> 2025 年卡车节海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>其他已确认在周末演出的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">Blossoms</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/franz-ferdinand">Franz Ferdinand</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sports-team">Sports Team</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fat-dog">Fat Dog</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maximo-park">Maximo Park</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/moonchild-sanelly">Moonchild Sanelly</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/natasha-bedingfield">娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德</a>也被确认为特邀嘉宾。</p><p>音乐节观众还可以观看<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-reytons">The Reytons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hard-life">Hard Life</a> 、Lime Garden、Corella、Only The Poets、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luvcat">Luvcat</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chloe-slater">Chloe Slater</a> 、Daydreamers、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardinals">Cardinals</a> 、Esme Emerson、Polly Money、Seb Lowe、Home Counties、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scouting-for-girls">Scouting For Girls</a>等乐队的演出和宾客名单。</p><p>节日经理 Lily Brimble 和营销主管 Sam Harris 谈到了 2025 年的活动：“我们非常高兴能够通过卡车 2025 的第一个细节来揭示我们在卡车总部所做的工作！就像我们最喜欢的乐队、伙伴以及我们在办公室里提出的每一个荒谬想法的一次盛大聚会一样——2025 年可能是我们迄今为止最完整的卡车周末活动。” </p><figure id="attachment_3815697" aria-describedby="caption-attachmen