-lord-of-the-rings-film-absolutely-no-plans-or-desires-to-be-a-part-of-it-3801422">最近也排除了回归</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-lord-of-the-rings">《指环王》系列饰演埃尔隆德的可能性</a></em>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hugo-weaving-is-coming-back-for-more-slow-horses-3815699">雨果·维文 (Hugo Weaving) 即将回归，带来更多“慢马”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
